What you need to know:

This year Rosa Associati Management who are the organisers of the annual race scaled down the competition to only four categories which includes the junior women 6km, junior men 8km, senior women and men 10km races due to the coronavirus pandemicSamuel Kibet, Isaac Kibet and Levi Kiprotich are some of the invited athletes from Rosa Management Camp in Kapchorwa, Uganda who will be competing in the raceAccording to Technical Director David Letting who is also a coach said that preparations are complete and they will be expecting a huge number of athletes after a long break due to the Covid-19 virus